[spaceship] AppAnalytics: support for impressions (and some comments + doc additions) (#14167)

- Added comments to the different metrics, so it becomes more obvious what information the user can receive. 
- Added support for the "new" impressions metrics add last year (?).

As interim documentation, how to use/test App Analytics:
1) Login: `Spaceship::Tunes.login("apple@id.com", "password")`
2) Select live app: `app = Spaceship::Tunes::Application.find("com.test.app")` 
3) Start analytics: `analytics = app.analytics`
4) Get "new" impressions metric: `impressions = analytics.app_impressions`

